{{main|David Attenborough}}

The following is a chronological list of television series and individual programmes where Sir [[David Attenborough]] is credited as writer, presenter, narrator or producer. In a career spanning seven decades, Attenborough's name has become synonymous with the [[nature documentary|natural history programmes]] produced by the [[BBC Natural History Unit]].

