[[Ohio Valley Wrestling]] has held a variety of [[professional wrestling tournament]]s competed for by wrestlers that are a part of their [[Ohio Valley Wrestling#Roster|roster]].
==Queen of OVW / Miss OVW Contest== The Queen of OVW / Miss OVW contest is a contest where a couple of female wrestlers in OVW (Ohio Valley Wrestling) are chosen and compete in several competitions. In the finals of the contest, the fans vote for the winner. The inaugural winner was [[ODB (wrestler)|ODB]] who is also the first ever [[OVW Women's Championship|OVW Women's Champion]]. The latest winner is Lovely Lylah who defeated [[Jessie Belle Smothers|Jessie Belle]], Ray Lynn and [[Taeler Hendrix]] in the finals of the 2013 contest.
